      %p
        Is your summer holiday getting closer?
        Have you begun to finalise all your must have items that will accompany you on this very important and much needed vacation?
        Expectations can be high once you have made it to your holiday destination, so you really need to know that you made all the right choices when packing.
        Are we really thinking it through before we jet off to enjoy our fun filled time in the sun?
        For instance, I can’t help wondering how many people give enough attention to their summer beach bag.
        This is the bag that will possibly support you for the entire holiday
        so why is it often forgotten about, or why do we reach for anything that will do and squeeze it into our suitcases right at the last minute?
        So, I am here to help you.

