        Knowing your essential items is going to ensure that your day on the beach runs smoothly.
        You do not want to be walking around in the hot sun looking for a shop to buy more sun cream and being faced with beach front prices because you have no other option.
        And you do not want to be getting burnt whilst you wander around trying to find some.
        To save on forgetting things I try to have a list of essential items that I need and would be a little bit stuck abroad without them.
        Here are my top 5 essential items that I never go without:

