    .article-text

      %p
        When the sun is up you want to be out there making the most of it.
        Constantly unpacking and repacking your beach bag and searching for that essential item when all you want to do is enjoy the beach can be frustrating.
        To save wasting time I use a quick list stored on my phone to check I have placed everything I need in my beach bag before I go.
        Now I can go ahead and relax knowing I have it all covered.
        Here is my quick list to help you get started:

